- [ ] Searching "soup" also matches (English still works)
- [ ] Tag suggestions show when typing Polish terms (e.g., "zu" shows soup/zupa)
- [ ] `filterRecipes` benefits automatically from expanded `resolveNormalizedTagTexts`

